sentences: After opening his first own workshop in 1969 he developed an individual strutting system for the interior of his instruments.
Since the early 1980s until shortly before his death in 2007 the master worked together with his son Paulino Bernabe II, who took over the workshop from his father.
1974 Bernabe was awarded the Gold Medal at the International Crafts Exhibition in Munich (Germany).
Video with photos of Paulino Bernabe Senior (2009).
